snippet.title: Debi Dooms
snippet.description:
A Brazilian Canadian girl from Canada. I’m a Paralegal and my goal with this channel is to use my knowledge to discuss things I am passionate about, in the pursuit of justice. Always with a sense of humour! I hope to connect with like minded individuals, and to make a difference, whether it’s through sharing my knowledge of the law, or simply making you laugh or smile. Sometimes we may discuss heavier topics and sometimes things may be more light hearted. 

I am so grateful that you decided to stop by and I hope you decide to join our little squad. If you have any ideas for videos, PLEASE let me know. My email is in every description box. If you have a story that you want to get out or a topic that the media won’t discuss but you feel should be.. PLEASE let me know! I want to amplify voices that deserve a platform to be heard. ❤️❤️❤️
